---
title: Sesame Shrimp with Ginger Scallion Rice and Crispy Green Beans
description: If you’re like us, you’ve seen a lot of stir-fries in your day. But thanks to our sweet hoisin marinade, aromatic rice, and sprinkle of nutty sesame seeds, this one is bound to top them all. Even the pickiest of eaters will love it. Sounds like a win-win to us.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w22-r3-b18719a4.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/w22-r3-556b94f3.pdf
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 550 kcal
  fat: 12 g
  saturated fat: 1.5 g
  carbohydrates: 75 g
